finalPattern.pattern_name: Triadic price-bracket videos framed as 'Cheapest vs. Most Expensive vs. Homemade' with a challenge mechanic reliably outperform baseline by combining extreme price anchors with a relatable DIY control, creating clear stakes that boost CTR and sustain watch-time.
